gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 135, Rockets 130
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Rockets, 135-130, in overtime.  Donovan Mitchell led the way with 37 points, six assists and four 3PM for the Cavaliers, while Sam Merrill tallied a career-high 19 points in the victory.  Fred VanVleet tallied 27 points, eight rebounds, and 17 assists for the Rockets in the losing effort.  The Cavaliers improve to 14-13 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 13-11.
